Package: QuadratSampleGenerator
Title: Quadrat Random Sample Generator
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Freya", "Innes", , "finnes@zoology.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Function randomly selects the desired number of quadrats to be 
  sampled based on the given dimensions of the gridded study site, and plots a 
  map showing these quadrats. Input should not be a vector (integer value only).
